{"tid":2227697,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羈押者舉「五一」：中秋快樂","createTime":"2020-10-03T04:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T04:55:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03b31fcf65c3133da58e55c02f210d75de98d28e","tid":2227697,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:02:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201003/WJPE4VYQZJB4HMHFQ2LLLMGOKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201003%2FWJPE4VYQZJB4HMHFQ2LLLMGOKQ%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmW2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=9a34f5a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201003%2FWJPE4VYQZJB4HMHFQ2LLLMGOKQ%2F&h=2c2971f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201003/WJPE4VYQZJB4HMHFQ2LLLMGOKQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羈押者舉「五一」：中秋快樂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OsfH0kaHUUFM5TOT3tLxcZFkPs0=/1474x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/56I4ZEE5PNASXJAEIWMLNEI7RM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOsfH0kaHUUFM5TOT3tLxcZFkPs0%3D%2F1474x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F56I4ZEE5PNASXJAEIWMLNEI7RM.jpg&h=2bea275b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多名羈留人士伸手出外，做出五一手勢，又大叫「中秋節快樂！」互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。。，有市民在街上回應並拍照上載社交媒體，獲大批網民留言及讚好支持，形成一個獄外與獄內的無形互動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拒社工全程陪同 叫錯性別耽誤服藥  警濫捕 智障男失控圖自殘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「好難捱呀」<br />\n<br />\n有市民表示，昨傍晚行經荔枝角收押所，發現其中一幢建築物，竟有六至八名羈留人士從不同窗台位置同時伸手出外，做出「五大訴求，缺一不可」的五一手勢，並且對外大叫「中秋節快樂」，其間更有人呼叫「好難捱呀」。當時身處收押所外的市民見到這感人一幕，有人拍下照片；有人大叫回應「中秋節快樂，（手足）頂住呀！」雙方互叫口號歷時10分鐘，其後疑懲教署人員發現阻止下才終止。<br />\n<br />\n有關相片上載至facebook後，隨即獲同路人留言「手足們撐住，我們沒有忘記你們」、「既感動又難過」。<br />\n<br />\n荔枝角收押所主要收押經法庭審訊，但被拒絕保釋還押監房，以及等待法官判決的犯人。"},{"pid":"264822e8fd77cf3d0cd13ccd01475114889f0a4b","tid":2227697,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2506e74c16a3c48060c56b94055609ad58389f0","tid":2227697,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"一個垃圾政權"},{"pid":"d960a9c6243aa8b122f8462ade4089985a09a8f9","tid":2227697,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"五一！！！！！"},{"pid":"4f1ec4a2b01fc37c550a8de591f70ac080625fb8","tid":2227697,"uid":271807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"既感動，更慚愧<br />\n<br />\n就算有朝一日要入黎，亦堅持同行"},{"pid":"c4c556f1676e5d19714b05022f6ee7583b2e11ef","tid":2227697,"uid":128570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足"},{"pid":"6b522eb353042979d845ba9bd7d844a4b933f115","tid":2227697,"uid":73276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"畫面好感人"},{"pid":"6b438140bf953808772adfb42ee548854e9a38ef","tid":2227697,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"save12hkyouths"},{"pid":"e0941fb491d883d6317dfa3c725d9a1b697a25c0","tid":2227697,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}